OL,3,C'An absolute travesty': Food banks
OL,4,Cface record demand for services
OL,6,Fthree main food banks have seen an
OL,7,F"exponential" rise in users since 2021
OL,8,Fand are now facing record demand.
OL,10,FThe St Vincent de Paul, Salvation Army
OL,11,Fand Grace's Trust give those in need
OL,12,Faccess to free food and electricity.
OL,14,FFigures from the last three years show
OL,15,Fthat demand at two of the island's
OL,16,Ffood banks has almost tripled.
OL,18,FOne woman who spoke to ITV News
OL,19,Fanonymously has used a food bank every
OL,20,Fweek for the last year and says it is
OL,21,Fa lifeline.
