OL,3,C'An absolute travesty': Food banks
OL,4,Cface record demand for services
OL,6,FShe explained: "I didn't expect one
OL,7,Fday to use a food bank. You go to the
OL,8,Fsupermarket with #20 and once you've
OL,9,Fbought three or four items you've
OL,10,Fspent that straight away."
OL,12,FThe St Vincent de Paul food bank has
OL,13,Fseen a rise of 168% in people needing
OL,14,Ftheir help since 2022.
OL,16,FNumber of users at St Vincent de Paul
OL,17,Ffood bank:
OL,19,FSinead Wright works for the charity
OL,20,Fand believes the demand will continue
OL,21,Fto rise.
