OL,3,C'An absolute travesty': Food banks
OL,4,Cface record demand for services
OL,6,FShe said: "We've already gone through
OL,7,F50% of our electricity vouchers in the
OL,8,Ffirst quarter, so we're where we would
OL,9,Fexpect to be in June and that's
OL,10,Fbecause of the rise in the cost of
OL,11,Felectricity. The demand is
OL,12,Fexponential."
OL,14,FJersey's Social Security Minister,
OL,15,FDeputy Lyndsay Feltham, has promised
OL,16,Ftackling the issue is one of her
OL,17,Fpriorities.
