OL,3,C'An absolute travesty': Food banks
OL,4,Cface record demand for services
OL,6,FShe explained: "It's an absolute
OL,7,Ftravesty that an island such as
OL,8,FJersey, a wealthy island, sees this
OL,9,Famount of poverty.
OL,11,F"I am taking some time to meet with
OL,12,Fthe charities that are involved in
OL,13,Fthis and learn first-hand from them
OL,14,Fabout the people using their
OL,15,Ffacilities and the reasons why they're
OL,16,Fusing them so that we can go to those
OL,17,Froot causes."
